{"tid":2032293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你班黃絲永遠唔會買到樓","createTime":"2020-05-24T03:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T05:48:44.000Z","uid":146880,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2aacf7ee7a91f906b504bbd81c4b405b1197f5c9","tid":2032293,"uid":146880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:51:05.000Z","msg":"尋晚尖沙咀上Anthony Sir 港樓堂，佢嬲嬲地講左一句：「年青果班個腦Short左， 想不勞而獲， 又唔識方法，佢地永遠唔會買到樓！」<br />\n我仲忍到佢， 後來中原果個深藍Brian Sir仲曬：「我上年先係灣仔買到500萬樓， 你唔出去搵姐！出去搞事果班真係廢物黎。」<br />\n我即刻忍唔撚住離開左，真係頂唔順，點解自己要比成萬銀聽佢兩條廢藍up野。<br />\n各位手足，認住佢地，就係佢地有份搞到香港今日咁！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sk7DZZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSk7DZZA.jpg&h=4db3959f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/31dPncV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F31dPncV.jpg&h=328518ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Do3S4rh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDo3S4rh.jpg&h=1a80ee97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60c92fe30b0d8945d07f9b7e1b86640dba6b9ed7","tid":2032293,"uid":258598,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:54:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e2950b292f2cce5dfb0c41e878e4d49f47af61a","tid":2032293,"uid":146880,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"60c92fe30b0d8945d07f9b7e1b86640dba6b9ed7","tid":2032293,"uid":258598,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:54:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:56:30.000Z","msg":"呢位巴手，你為左賺果5毛，可以去到幾盡？"},{"pid":"3922d407cf5c1411c8103d4e13405773e1d256ca","tid":2032293,"uid":57308,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e2950b292f2cce5dfb0c41e878e4d49f47af61a","tid":2032293,"uid":146880,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"60c92fe30b0d8945d07f9b7e1b86640dba6b9ed7","tid":2032293,"uid":258598,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:5