ts/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wzkyfKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwzkyfKW.jpg&h=59c500bd&s={SIZE}\" /> 龍市！龍市"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:48:31.000Z","msg":"係屈機嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ZZ3CZw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ZZ3CZw.jpg&h=87b15e92&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n樓，車，女人， 咩都有"},{"pid":"957ee3883d4b075471b487000249f512e0411440","tid":2032293,"uid":146880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:35:34.000Z","msg":"佢本書有寫，係唔係真就唔知。<br />\nAnthony Sir西環出生，以前係TVB寫兩性專題節目， 之後搞賓館、美容、 骨場、 製作公司都生意失敗，炒股票輸到仆街欠左一筆高利貸。之後香港樓市起飛， 不理屋企人反對，祖屋都賣埋搵到第一桶金， 然後不停炒樓，炒到成億身家。<br />\n炒樓期間聯埋班炒家做市，炒高曬幾個九龍樓盤， 開班教人炒樓，萬尻幾蚊一個課程，教人集資炒骨場，酒店和工廈，之前傳媒登高佢D仆街野， 但最後冇事，繼續開班呃尻人。<br />\n近年，佢仲聯同搞埋大陸佬呃D同學買大陸樓，好多同學跟左佢買左都血本無歸，仲要收貴服務費，拍晒片扮晒專家叫人買，自己又唔買。<br />\n佢真魔鬼黎， 係食人血饅頭。"},{"pid":"b2f07c2379a942dd2720341d09a0512609121aab","tid":2032293,"uid":48604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"萬幾銀上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}